# Google Reviews Sentiment Tracker â€“ Power BI Project

## Overview
This Power BI dashboard visualises customer sentiment based on Google Reviews. It performs text-based sentiment analysis to classify reviews as Positive, Neutral, or Negative, and tracks sentiment trends over time.

## Features
- Extracted Google Reviews using Python web scraping
- Performed sentiment classification and trend tracking
- Designed an interactive Power BI dashboard with dynamic filters
- Weekly auto-refresh capability to update sentiment insights

## Tools Used
- Power BI (Data Visualization & Dashboard Design)
- Python (Data Extraction & Sentiment Analysis)
- Excel (Data Cleaning and Preprocessing)

## Usage
Open the `.pbix` file in Power BI Desktop to explore the dashboard. Sample data is included for demonstration.

